export default class {
  login = [
    { name: "email", type: "input" },
    { name: "password", type: "input" },
  ]

  register = [
    { name: "firstName", type: "input" },
    { name: "lastName", type: "input" },
    { name: "email", type: "input" },
    { name: "password", type: "input" },
    { name: "organisationName", type: "input" },
    { name: "organisationKind", type: "select", options: [1, 2, 3] },
  ]

  addCustomer = [
    { name: "name", type: "input" },
    { name: "organisationNr", type: "input" },
    { name: "vatNr", type: "input" },
    { name: "reference", type: "input" },
    { name: "paymentTerm", type: "input" },
    { name: "website", type: "input" },
    { name: "email", type: "input" },
    { name: "phoneNumber", type: "input" },
  ]
  async editCustomer(userKit, id, values) {
    return userKit.updateCustomer(id, values)
  }
}
